    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i'd rather not go to the clinic if i don't have to, it's such a hassle and expensive. if i just stick to the ice and elevation and maybe take some ibuprofen, do you think it'll definitely be okay in a couple of days? i really don't think i need an x-ray if the swelling goes down.",
