      "content": "i just tried to walk on it with the ibuprofen and it's still super painful, like a sharp bone pain. but the swelling is definitely going down a bit. if i just wrap it tight with an ace bandage and keep it iced, isn't that basically the same thing as what they'd do at the doctor anyway? i feel like i can manage this at home if i just stay off it for a week.",
